Simplify and Factor Allegations

allegations <- read_csv('data/allegation_categories.csv')
## Parsed with column specification:
## cols(
##   allegation = col_character(),
##   count = col_double(),
##   allegation_category = col_character()
## )
allegations <- allegations %>% 
  select(allegation, allegation_category)

nypd <- nypd %>% 
  left_join(allegations, BY = 'allegation') 
## Joining, by = "allegation"
nypd <- nypd %>% 
  filter(is.na(allegation_category) == FALSE)


nypd$allegation_category <- factor(nypd$allegation_category, levels = c('Refusal to Comply', 'Offensive Language/Gesture', 'Search', 'Stop or Question', 'Threaten', 'Physical Assault', 'Gun Involved', 'Other'))

Visualize Data

Demographics of Misconduct Victims

My_Theme = theme(
  title = element_text(size = 16),
  axis.title.x = element_text(size = 16),
  axis.text.x = element_text(size = 14),
  axis.text.y = element_text(size = 12),
  axis.title.y = element_text(size = 16),
  legend.text = element_text(size=12))

nypd %>% 
  filter(year_received < 2020 & year_received >= 2000) %>% 
  #filter(victim_ethnicity != 'Unknown') %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = year_received, fill = victim_ethnicity)) +
  geom_bar(position = 'fill') +
  labs(title = "Victims of NYPD Police Misconduct By Ethnicity",
       x = "Year", 
       y = "Proportion of Misconduct Allegations",
       fill = "Victim Ethnicity") +
  geom_vline(xintercept = 2012.5, col = 'red', lwd = 1.5) +
  geom_text(aes(x=2013, label="Stop and Frisk banned in 2013", y=0.5), colour="white", angle=270, vjust = .6, size = 5) +
  theme_scientific() +
  scale_fill_brewer(palette = "Dark2") +
  My_Theme

Top Offenders

top_offenders <- nypd %>% 
  group_by(unique_mos_id) %>% 
  summarize(victim_count = n()) 



precinct_counts <- nypd %>% 
  distinct(unique_mos_id, precinct) %>% 
  group_by(unique_mos_id) %>% 
  summarize(precinct_count = n())

nypd <- left_join(nypd, top_offenders, by = 'unique_mos_id')
nypd <- left_join(nypd, precinct_counts, by = 'unique_mos_id')
nypd <- nypd %>% 
  mutate(victims_per_precinct = victim_count / precinct_count) %>% 
  mutate(offender_level = ifelse(victim_count >= 20, 'Serial Offender', 'Standard Offender'))

nypd$offender_level <- factor(nypd$offender_level, levels = c('Standard Offender', 'Serial Offender'))

nypd %>% 
  group_by(unique_mos_id, first_name, last_name, victim_count) %>% 
  select(first_name, last_name, victim_count) %>% 
  unique() %>% 
  arrange(desc(victim_count)) %>% 
  head(10) %>% 
  kable() %>% 
  kable_styling()

Average Number of Victims Targeted by Serial Offenders

nypd %>% 
  group_by(unique_mos_id, victim_ethnicity, offender_level) %>% 
  summarize(victim_count = n()) %>% 
  group_by(victim_ethnicity, offender_level) %>% 
  summarize(avg_victim_count = mean(victim_count)) %>% 
  filter(victim_ethnicity != 'Unknown') %>% 
  ggplot(aes(y = avg_victim_count, x = offender_level, fill = victim_ethnicity, width = .6)) +
  geom_bar(stat = 'identity', position = position_dodge(width = .65)) +
    labs(title = "Average Number of Victims By Ethnicity",
      x = "Offender Level", 
      y = "Victim Count",
      fill = 'Victim Ethnicity') +
  theme_scientific() +
  scale_fill_brewer(palette = "Dark2") +
  My_Theme

nypd %>% 
  group_by(unique_mos_id, precinct, offender_level) %>% 
  summarize(count = n()) %>% 
  group_by(offender_level) %>% 
  summarize(precinct_average = mean(count)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(y = precinct_average, x = offender_level, fill = offender_level)) +
  geom_bar(stat = 'identity') +
    labs(title = "Average Number of Precincts Moves By Offender Level",
      x = "Offender Level",

Map

precinct_totals <- nypd %>%
  filter(year_received < 2020 & year_received >= 2000) %>% 
  group_by(precinct) %>% 
  summarize(count = n()) %>% 
  arrange(desc(count)) %>% 
  head(76)

# JOIN WITH GPS DATA
mapdata <- gps_precinct %>% 
  left_join(precinct_totals, by = 'precinct')


pal <- colorNumeric(
  palette = colorRampPalette(c('steelblue4', 'red'))(length(mapdata$count)), 
  domain = mapdata$count)

qpal <- colorQuantile(pal(mapdata$count), mapdata$count, n = 5)

popup <- paste("<strong> Precinct ",as.character(mapdata$precinct), 
                     "</strong>", 
                     "<br/>",
                     "<strong>Misconduct Allegations: ", as.character(mapdata$count),"</strong>")

interactive_map <- mapdata %>% 
  leaflet() %>% 
  addTiles() %>% 
  addCircleMarkers(lng = ~Lat,
                   lat = ~Lon, fillOpacity = .7, 
                   color = ~pal(count), 
                   radius = ~sqrt(count)/1.5, 
                   stroke = FALSE,
                   popup = popup) %>% 
  addLegend(position = "bottomright", 
            pal = pal, 
            values = ~count, 
            opacity = 1,
            title = "Total Misconduct Allegations")

interactive_map
